menu "AirCube Configuration"

config AIRCUBE_ZB_TX_POWER_DBM
    int "Zigbee TX power (dBm)"
    range -24 20
    default 20
    help
        Requested Zigbee transmit power in dBm for the native 802.15.4 radio.
        Actual applied power may be clamped by hardware, SDK, or regional limits.
        Default is the chip maximum (20 dBm) for best link margin; reduce if
        you need lower power consumption or to satisfy regional EIRP limits.

endmenu
